title: Match History Help
body: I cant find my match history on this page. help

replies.body:
You can find NA Match History either inside the game client or from the [**Match History Web Page**](http://matchhistory.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-history).

Let me know if this helped!
i tried clicking on the "match history web" ling, but all i see is this https://gyazo.com/d8e9f6906fdf8de37d1e4b43d025ffac

Ah, this is a known bug with the match history web page. We're looking into it, but I'm unable to provide a timeline on when it will be fixed. You can report this one our [**Bug Tracker**](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/bug-report) if you'd like.

If you have any other questions, let me know.
